## Complexity Analysis

| Operation             | Time Complexity |
| --------------------- | --------------- |
| Visit every node once | O(n)            |

**Time Complexity:** `O(n)`

Reason:

* Every node is inserted into the queue once.
* Every node is removed from the queue once.

---

**Space Complexity:** `O(n)`

Reason:

* The queue may contain all nodes of one level.
* The answer list also stores all nodes.

